==============================================================================
Documentation for the topos compiler


Inside the /src, you can see there are lots of directories, it has its own
meaning. And it groups codes with similar function into one. For example,

The source code of the Topos tokeniser is located entirely under `Tokenising`
directory. And parsing rules is located under `Parsing`.

Some of the data that will be used in entire compilation lifetime is located
under this path, which is src/.
